{"tid":656433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再贏]奧林巴斯將撤出在華相機相關生産","createTime":"2018-05-07T09:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T09:36:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a784282432d575b7e4b0e45d6a4ed54550b78039","tid":656433,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/itelectric-appliance/30371-2018-05-07-15-54-36.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Findustry%2Fitelectric-appliance%2F30371-2018-05-07-15-54-36.html&d=4tRPLw2x%2Bopihp7tnb4LpQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4a18eaa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/itelectric-appliance/30371-2018-05-07-15-54-36.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本奧林巴斯5月7日宣佈，將撤出在華生産數位相機相關産品的業務。<br />\n<br />\n伴隨智慧手機的普及，數位相機市場不斷縮縮小，奧林巴斯的中國生産子公司將停産。為提升效率，將把生産基地向越南集中。據悉，伴隨撤出産生的臨時費用將計入合併財報，具體金額正在計算之中。"},{"pid":"3954cbcb9387afaeec08ed0fab5095d723130abf","tid":656433,"uid":147233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:20:40.000Z","msg":"睇錯奧巴馬"},{"pid":"07ce927ede2871d09e1b66e8ee5ed0ae7c07970a","tid":656433,"uid":9398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"小日本撒出蟈國，蟈國自行研發哈勃即影即用相機。又贏"},{"pid":"2dd35eb8fe644fe93725f66fe764973574e688f3","tid":656433,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"中囯抗戰勝利, 小日本夾住尾巴走"},{"pid":"76ba1c27b0b9238481cb0e99b1e7bebe6141a2ef","tid":656433,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"中國又羸"},{"pid":"8715908eb778e98eec921668970966ddac897104","tid":656433,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:30:11.000Z","msg":"中國人用小米影相便可"},{"pid":"bbd7d67f7cb8c56f601363b2ba575b7380efdf24","tid":656433,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:30:25.000Z",